THE ladies showed what their Mama gave them.  They are not shy to rock up in mini-skirts and “veza ithanga” in any social event.  And they are women of all size, from plus size women, average and slender.  This is exactly what happened at Disoufeng Pub and Restaurant in Meadowlands, Soweto, when it was hosting the Firstwatch Entrepreneur Challenge on Sunday evening.  The ladies rocked up in their short pants and skirts. 